  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to test the impact of a bundled NOHARM Conversation Guide with&#xD;
      clinical decision support intervention embedded within an Electronic Health Record (EHR) on&#xD;
      pain and function 3 months following surgery.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
